exports[`shared-types template > renders a shared types page 1`] = `
"---
title: "Types"
titleStyle: code
description: "Shared type definitions — v0.8.0"
---

## Overview

Shared TypeScript types used across the \`@qvac/sdk\` API.

### \`ModelType\`

Supported model types.

\`\`\`typescript
type ModelType = "llm" | "embed" | "tts"
\`\`\`

| Member | Description |
| --- | --- |
| \`llm\` | Large language model |
| \`embed\` | Embedding model |

---

### \`CachePolicy\`

Cache eviction policies.

\`\`\`typescript
type CachePolicy = "lru" | "fifo"
\`\`\`"
`;
